On sand dunes surrounding salt water lake 500 m from sea. Location is on coast south of Amboasary which is 75 km W. of Ft Dauphin on main road. Soil is pure sand, off-white in colour. Dunes are generally shrub-covered to a ht. of 2 m. and give way, inland to Didiera bush. Forest Reserve, private, owned by Heanlure family. At Berenty on flood plain of R. Mandraray, approx. 100 km. W. of Ft Dauphin. Forest type restricted to narrow belt either side of river. Higher land has Didiera scrub. Soil is brown and sandy, deep and freely drained.
